User Story: Smart Chatbot with Memory

Step 0: Learn the Basics
- Read FastAPI docs (focus on basics , Auth, streaming, Architecture)
- Explore OpenAI API docs (Chat + Assistants+ Tools+ Function)
- Check out Mem0 docs (memory layer)

Step 1: Build Core Chatbot
Backend: FastAPI with streaming OpenAI responses
- Real-time chat responses
- Smart system prompts
- Clean API design

Frontend: Simple React + TypeScript chat interface
- Live message streaming
- Simple Ui and Easy to use


 Step 2: Add Memory
Smart Memory: Integrate Mem0 to remember users using tool calls
- Store important conversation details
- Retrieve relevant memories automatically
- Let users see what the bot remembers